snippet.title: Morkredd - One-week game jam result
snippet.description: Last week we attended the "Norwegian Championship in Gameplay" with this concept called "Morkredd". The game is a multiplayer co-op puzzler where you need to keep out of any shadows to stay alive. We're really pleased with the result, and plan on developing the game further. Thanks to Bendik Høydahl for helping us with audio!
